      <title>财政部在关税揭幕之前与欧洲的反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/treasuries-gain-as-trade-tensions-rise-ahead-of-trump-s-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国政府债券删除了五年财政部票据以来10月以来的最低水平的收益，该收益率提高了欧洲政府债券收益率，此前该债券的收益率上升了，该报告称该集团正准备对任何新的关税做出回应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/treasuries-gain-as-trade-tensions-rise-ahead-of-trump-s-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 10:46:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
